{"type": "article", "id": 10073, "title": "把流汗拍出大片感，佳得乐也是很拼", "description": "抱住“乔丹”和“流汗”，佳得乐的营销能做几辈子。", "date": "2015-05-27T11:09:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6461, "name": "乔丹"}, {"id": 8076, "name": "佳得乐"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702123640ri5CYuLyAExo7mIZ.jpg", "contents": "\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style>@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"宋体\";\r\n}@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"Cambria Math\";\r\n}@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"@宋体\";\r\n}@font-face {\r\n  font-family: \"Cambria\";\r\n}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal { margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; }.MsoChpDefault { font-family: Cambria; }div.WordSection1 { page: WordSection1; }</style>\r\n</head>\n<body>\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> \r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">飞人乔丹曾说过，每一滴汗水的价值不同 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(not all sweat is created equal)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\"> 。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">换句话说，在运动的极致中挥洒的汗水如金子般宝贵，不是大太阳晒出来的能比的。作为品牌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 50 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">周年“致敬乔丹”活动的一部分（我们之前也曾<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/7650.html\">报道</a>过），运动饮料品牌佳得乐拍以“酷爱流汗”拍摄了一支大片。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y01546e9r6i&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"498\" width=\"640\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">发</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">明佳得乐的初衷即为了运动员在补充剧烈运动中流失的水分和无机盐。而佳得乐对于这一品牌概念的贯彻堪称执着，希望你一流汗就想喝佳得乐，看到佳得乐就想流汗。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123640pkQtxezCKy4guGBv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">去年，他们也曾在便利店内大玩整蛊，要求顾客必须要流汗才能购买佳得乐。并在店内安装针孔摄像头，将顾客们着急冒汗的样子拍下来，用这种方式提醒人们：任何时候都不要丧失流汗的能力，多运动——多喝，佳得乐。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div id=\"xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"display:none;\" id=\"__if72ru4sdfsdfrkjahiuyi_once\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"display:none;\" id=\"__hggasdgjhsagd_once\">\r\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}